td.div: English: Updated 2007 logo of El País, a major national newspaper in Spain, with new accent on the "i", adopted on 2007-10-21. The prior logo was the same but without the accent.

tr.td: 21 de septiembre de 2007 (primera publicación) (13 de noviembre de 2007 (fecha original de carga))

Converted to SVG by User:Closeapple using PDF2SVG (also described at [1]) and given 1% internal margin using Inkscape.
